text: FK Slovan Ivanka pri Dunaji is a Slovak football team, based in the town of Ivanka pri Dunaji. The club was founded in 1919. In year 2009 FK Slovan Ivanka pri Dunaji merged with club FO Trnávka. ==References== == External links == *Official website Category:Football clubs in Slovakia FK Slovan Ivanka pri Dunaji Category:Association football clubs established in 1919 FK Slovan Ivanka pri Dunaji
